11#ifndef COMMON_VIDEO_FRAME_COUNTS_H_
12#define COMMON_VIDEO_FRAME_COUNTS_H_
13
14namespace webrtc {
15
16struct FrameCounts {
17 FrameCounts() : key_frames(0), delta_frames(0) {}
18 int key_frames;
19 int delta_frames;
20};
21
22// Callback, used to notify an observer whenever frame counts have been updated.
23class FrameCountObserver {
24 public:
25 virtual ~FrameCountObserver() {}
26 virtual void FrameCountUpdated(const FrameCounts& frame_counts,
27 uint32_t ssrc) = 0;
28};
29
30} // namespace webrtc
31
32#endif // COMMON_VIDEO_FRAME_COUNTS_H_
